| phone | String | No |

---

# 10. Validation Rules

## Team

- Team name cannot be empty.
- Team name must be unique.
- Score cannot be negative.

---

## Member

- Full name required.
- Duplicate members not allowed.

---

## Event

- Registration deadline must be after event creation.
- Event must have a name.

---

# 11. Normalisation

A relational implementation would follow Third Normal Form (3NF).

Benefits include:

- Reduced redundancy
- Improved consistency
- Easier maintenance
- Better scalability

