# 18. Summary

The Friends Like These database provides a flexible and scalable data model capable of supporting real-time event management.

The Firebase implementation enables immediate synchronisation between clients while maintaining a simple data structure. The accompanying relational design demonstrates how the application can evolve into an enterprise-grade solution using a traditional SQL database.
